text:
Hi :wave: <@UJ0DLL62J> you can use this css for your custom width. Max width always work on table when you use fixed table layout.


table {
    table-layout: fixed;
    max-width: 600px !important;
    width: 100% !important;
}
#backgroundTable {
    margin: 0 auto !important;
}

Max-width doesn't work on *Outlook* :disappointed_relieved:, so  we can use  width and manage it with media query, update previous css with this new one.

table {
   table-layout: fixed;
   width: 600px !important;
}
#backgroundTable {
   margin: 0 auto !important;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            table {
                width: 100% !important;
            }
}
